reviewText: Another good serial type movie I saw as a kid back in the fifties. As I saw that amazon had many of these serials I decided to start my collection. Thanks to amazon I now have many of my favorites from the past and enjoy watching them all over again. Thanks Amazon.
This dvd is a full length feature version of the original serial.  This point should have been clarified in the initial description.  You had to read down in the specifics to find this out.
